"能力说明\n• 世界书会按条目规则注入上下文，帮助模型保持设定一致。\n• 它不等于记忆系统，不会自动学习新事实。\n\n在手表上怎么用\n1. 先确认会话已绑定目标世界书。\n2. 需要新增时可用 URL 导入。\n3. 查看“启用条目 x/y”判断每本世界书的生效密度。\n\n提示\n• 手表适合快速查看与基础操作；\n• 深度编辑建议在 iPhone 完成后同步。" = "What it does\n• Worldbooks inject context by entry rules to help the model keep settings consistent.\n• They are not the memory system and do not automatically learn new facts.\n\nHow to use on Apple Watch\n1. Make sure the session is bound to the target worldbook.\n2. Use URL import when you need to add one.\n3. Check Enabled entries x/y to understand how much of each worldbook is active.\n\nTips\n• Apple Watch is best for quick review and basic operations.\n• Do deeper editing on iPhone and sync afterward.";
"能力说明\n• 记忆系统会在回复前检索历史信息，提升连续性。\n• 写入开关仅影响“新增记忆”，不影响读取已有记忆。\n\n推荐流程\n1. 先开启总开关体验效果。\n2. 对噪声敏感时可先关闭写入，仅保留读取。\n3. 定期到记忆库管理清理低质量记忆。" = "What it does\n• The memory system retrieves historical information before replies to improve continuity.\n• The write switch affects only new memories and does not affect reading existing memories.\n\nRecommended flow\n1. Turn on the master switch first to try the effect.\n2. If you are sensitive to noise, disable writing first and keep reading only.\n3. Regularly clean low-quality memories in Memory Library Management.";
"覆盖浅色外观下的聊天文本颜色。" = "Override chat text color in light appearance.";
"覆盖深色外观下的聊天文本颜色。" = "Override chat text color in dark appearance.";
"让 AI 持续理解你的长期偏好和上下文。" = "Let AI continuously understand your long-term preferences and context.";
"语音朗读（TTS）" = "Speech playback (TTS)";
"这个页面适合做什么\n• 统一进入进阶功能，不打断主聊天流程。\n• 快速定位语音、工具集成、导入和维护能力。\n\n入口建议\n• 记忆系统 / 世界书：管理长期偏好与规则知识。\n• MCP / 快捷指令：接入外部能力和自动化流程。\n• 存储管理 / 远程文件访问：做维护与清理。\n\n使用建议\n• 先保证核心入口可用，再逐步开启实验功能。" = "What this page is for\n• Enter advanced features without interrupting the main chat flow.\n• Quickly find voice features, tool integrations, imports, and maintenance.\n\nEntry suggestions\n• Memory / Worldbooks: manage long-term preferences and rule knowledge.\n• MCP / Shortcuts: connect external capabilities and automation flows.\n• Storage Management / Remote File Access: perform maintenance and cleanup.\n\nTip\n• Make sure core entries work first, then enable experimental features gradually.";
"集中管理工具集成、语音能力与系统维护入口。" = "Manage tool integrations, voice features, and system maintenance entries in one place.";
"页面作用\n• 快速判断各类工具在“配置层”与“会话层”是否真正可用。\n\n指标怎么读\n• 配置已启用：你在设置里已经打开。\n• 当前会话实际可用：在总开关、审批策略、隔离策略后仍可用。\n\n推荐流程\n1. 先看汇总数字，确认问题范围。\n2. 开启“仅显示已启用”缩小排查范围。\n3. 进入具体工具页调整策略与状态。\n\n常见情况\n• 如果显示世界书隔离生效，记忆、MCP、Agent Skills、快捷指令可能被会话策略屏蔽。" = "What this page does\n• Quickly determine whether each tool category is actually available at the configuration and session levels.\n\nHow to read metrics\n• Configured enabled: turned on in settings.\n• Available in current session: still usable after master switches, approval policies, and isolation policies.\n\nRecommended flow\n1. Check summary numbers first to scope the issue.\n2. Enable Show Enabled Only to narrow the view.\n3. Enter specific tool pages to adjust policies and status.\n\nCommon case\n• If worldbook isolation is active, memory, MCP, Agent Skills, and Shortcuts may be blocked by session policy.";

